description: Number of inequivalent cyclic Hadamard difference sets with parameters (2^n-1, 2^(n-1)-1, 2^(n-2)-1).
references: P. Gaal (gaal(AT)scf.usc.edu) and S. W. Golomb, Exhaustive determination of (1023,511,255) cyclic Hadamard difference sets, Math. Comp. Math. Comp. 70 (2001), no. 233, 357-366.
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
